                    <p class="paragraph privacy__paragraph">If you have any comments on this policy, please email them to <a class="link privacy-description__link" href="mailto:hello@rebasegroup.com">hello@rebasegroup.com</a>. This policy contains the following information (you can access a specific section of this policy by clicking below):</p>
