                <div class="privacy-description">
                    <h3 class="privacy-description__heading">Who We Are</h3>
                    <p class="paragraph privacy__paragraph">Rebase Group Ltd is a limited company registered in England under company number 13016792. Our registered office is at: Castle House, Castle Street, Guildford, GU1 3UW.</p>
                    <p class="paragraph privacy__paragraph">If you wish to speak to someone about the policy, please contact us on <a class="link privacy-description__link" href="mailto:hello@rebasegroup.com">hello@rebasegroup.com</a>.</p>
                    <p class="paragraph privacy__paragraph">We respect your right to privacy and will only process personal information about you in accordance with applicable data protection laws. We comply with General Data Protection Regulation (2016/679) and the UK Data Protection Act 2018 (the “Data Protection Legislation”). If any of these laws are replaced or superseded, we will also comply with that.</p>
